HEADWORD: Indictable
<hw>In*dict"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Capable of
being, or liable to be, indicted; subject to indictment; <as>as, an
<ex>indictable</ex> offender or offense</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
